            <div id="slide2" class="mugshots text-center"><img src="/static/img/heroes/portraits/brewmaster_vert.jpg" width="210px"><p class="user-name">xxMLG820xx</p> <p class="mugshot-match-info"> Match 21164033085 <br> 30:35 Loss</p></div>


